reported from Imam Reza (a) that if any person is feared of his enemy and his enemy is powerful then if he recites YAA QAABE-ZO 1000 times daily for 3 nights then either his enemy will become friend or will be busy in his work and forget the enmity.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh agar koi shakhs apne dushman ka khouf rakhta ho aur us ka dushman qawi ho to agar woh 3 raat tak har raat ko 1000 martaba YAA QAABE-ZO ka vird kare to uska dushman ya to us ka dost ban jaayega ya us ki dushmani bhul kar idhar-udhar ke kaamo mein mashghool (buzy) ho jaayega.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ اگر کوئی شخص اپنے دشمن کا خوف رکھتا ہو اور اس کا دشمن قوی ہو تو اگر وہ 3 رات تک ہر رات کو 1000 بار ’’یَاقَابِضُ‘‘  کا ورد کرے تو اس کا دشمن یا تو اس کا دوست بن جائے گا یا اس کی دشمنی بھول کر ادھر اُدھر کے کاموں میں مشغول ہوجائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGree